# ECG Final Project

---

## Init Environment

```shell
poetry install
poetry env activate
./.venv/Scripts/activate
```

## Training Model

```shell
cd final
python train2.py
```

## Deploy Model as FastAPI App

```shell
python app.py
```

Deploy as 127.0.0.1:8000
